¬Improve access to resources for 3rd parties by utilising a hybrid cloud solution, powered by Microsoft Azure.  Role-based control ensures secure access to data, whilst supporting 3rd party products, to drive innovation as part of an advanced energy partner ecosystem.

¬Deliver a robust, highly available online presence that benefits from the processing power of the cloud and is entirely secure.  The Microsoft Azure cloud is elastic and automatically scales to support unexpected increases in traffic.  It provides a cost efficient solution, providing resources when needed, avoiding investment in infrastructure that's rarely fully utilised.

Microsoft's Azure cloud platform conforms to the strictest standards and adheres to regulatory requirements both in terms of technology and industry verticals.  Effortlessly benefit from extraordinary security measures that are managed with simplified role-based capabilities, that are baked right into the product.

Microsoft maintain platform integrity with a strictly controlled and tested approach to server patching and maintenance.  You don't have to worry about platform robustness, Microsoft will do that for you.
